## Quick Start

Create a mock file and put it in a folder called `mocks`

```json
[
    {
        "request": {
            "path": "/user/(d+)/slug/(.*)",
            "params": {
                "output_type": "json|xml"
            }
        },
        "response": {
            "status": 200,
            "headers": {
                "Content-Type": "application/json"
            },
            "body": [
                {
                    "id": "slug-id",
                    "content": "The post content"
                }
            ]
        }
    }
]
```

